**National Savings Certificate (NSC)** is a government-backed savings instrument offering 7.7% p.a. (Q1 FY 2026-27) with annual compounding over a 5-year tenure. NSC qualifies for Section 80C deduction on the principal, and the interest accrued annually is deemed reinvested and also qualifies for 80C. It is a safe, tax-efficient option for moderate-risk investors.
